thread.title: Etienne Spangenberg
thread.title_full: PACK & SEND Australia reviewed by Etienne Spangenberg

author: Etienne Spangenberg
title: Etienne Spangenberg
text: We moved to Sydney recently and had 6 boxes to ship. We used the self service option (printed out own labels out etc). Boxes were collected on the nominated day and swiftly delivered to our new home! Excellent rates and service! Will definitely recommend and use again!
